users.sign:
Join my group - 100474!

📣 Updated 14th June 2016 📣

Hi Palfishers!

🎉 JUNE PROMOTION 🎉

[THIS MONTH THERE IS A DISCOUNT FOR IELTS STUDENTS AND ANYONE WHO CALLS ME MORE THAN 4 DAYS A WEEK!

YOU GET AN EXCLUSIVE RATE OF ¥1.5!]

I am currently focussing on IELTS and preparing a whole set of Live Classes specifically for IELTS students. 

[Price Increase]

It's with a heavy heart that I will need to increase my price to 1.6. I have been extremely competitively priced ever since I started in Nov' 2015 and I think this new price is a fair reflection of my teaching abilities and reputation on PalFish.

[There is a possibility that if you visit me on a regular basis that we can come to an agreement on price. It will depend on how frequently you would like to learn from me.]

Thank you so much for your attention in this matter and for understanding and respecting my position.

非常感谢你

*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*

📕 CLASSES I OFFER 📕

You'll notice that I don't offer lesson packages. This is because you can learn anything you want from me, including:

-GRAMMAR 

Verb Tenses, Verb Patterns, Adjectives, Adverbs, Reported Speech, Conditionals, Articles, Indicative, Imperative, Subjunctive, Prepositions, Modals, Gerunds & Infinitives, Relative Clauses.

-IELTS (See below.)

-VOCABULARY, SYNONYMS & ANTONYMS

I have a huge vocabulary and will be happy to provide you with amazing techniques at remembering words.

-PRONUNCIATION (English RP)

Masterclass in British pronunciation with amazing techniques you'll have never seen before.

-IDIOMS, SLANG, PHRASES & PROVERBS

I have a great 3 step method for teaching any of these. I'll be happy to show you in a lesson.

-CULTURE

Having travelled extensively, I can teach you the cultural differences from many countries from around the world. I specialize in British culture, but know lots about other cultures too.

-SPANISH, FRENCH & THAI

I speak, read and write these fluently and am able to teach them to a high level. I will be happy to demonstrate in a lesson.

-GEOGRAPHY, HISTORY, ASTRONOMY

I also specialize in these subjects and it would be my pleasure to increase your knowledge of these subjects.

-MOVIES, TV, MUSIC & SINGING

With a background as an actor and professional singer, it'll be my pleasure to discuss these topics at length.

*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*

📖 IELTS EXPERTISE 📖

I am currently focussing on helping students pass their IELTS exams.

IELTS is something that I specialize in.

Are you stuck on band 5.0 or 5.5 and need to get 6.5? Or do you need to increase your grade from 6.0 to 7.0?
You have come to the right teacher! I have extensive experience in helping people improve their score.

Here are the reasons why you should choose me to be your IELTS teacher:

- I have experience in helping people improve their band (score).
- I have a HUGE amount of IELTS materials I will share with you.
- I will teach you my amazing strategy for Part 2 of the speaking exam which really makes it a lot easier.
- I focus on many areas: Vocabulary, Grammar, Idioms, Pronunciation and, most importantly, STAYING CALM.
- I'll provide you with the model (band 9) answer to show you what that looks like.
- I know how IELTS examiners decide what score to give you.
- I'm available on PalFish 10+ hours a day, 6 days a week.
- I have taught for over 4 months and have over 1000 hours of teaching experience on PalFish.
- I used an extremely efficient method of teaching which means you get the most for your money.

Please contact me for a consultation and I will be able to show you how I can help you prepare in the best possible way for IELTS and dramatically improve your scores.

(I am also still happy to talk to students for any other topics and even if you're not taking IELTS please feel free to contact me! I really look forward to hearing from you soon.)

My personal introduction continues below...

*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*

🌏 ABOUT ME 🌏

Hi there!
I am Dan. I am 34 years old and I am from London, England.
I have been a private tutor for university and afterschool students for 10 years.
I have a deep passion for Asian culture and I love travelling throughout Asia whenever I get the chance.
I speak four languages : English, Spanish, French & Thai. 

If I am honest, I do not speak a lot of Chinese (maybe 10 words!) but I am definitely trying to learn as much Chinese as I can! It's quite hard!

Languages and culture are extremely interesting to me and I spend a lot of my free time learning as much as I can about cultures from all over the world.
Travelling is a great passion of mine and I have travelled to 37 countries worldwide. 

I always make every effort to interact with the local people and really get immersed in their lifestyle and culture. I don't want to be a tourist, I want to live how they live, eat what they eat and get to know them as well as I can.

Teaching and education are very important to me and I spend a lot of time developing new and interesting ways to teach my students.
I think the most important aspect of being a good teacher is to be engaging. If you can really get to know a student well, understand what they need and, most importantly - be understood, then helping them learn a new language should be an easy thing to achieve.

My students become my friends and I care about them. I want them to achieve and be successful.
I will structure how I teach for each of my friends, because I want them to get the best out of their time with me.
I also think it is very important to help build confidence in people's English speaking abilities. 

Too many people are worried that they'll say the wrong thing or make mistakes. Making mistakes is just a natural part of learning a new language. I made many mistakes when I started learning to speak new languages. It's by learning from these mistakes and taking onboard the corrections that we really become good at speaking the language.

From my experience of speaking several languages the BEST way to get good at a given language is to practice. 
Practice, practice, practice. Find people that speak that language well and practice as much as you can with them.
It doesn't matter that you might not be perfect. What does matter is that you strive to improve your speaking ability.

Originally I wanted to be a psychologist and I did a lot of research in psychology, so I believe I can understand how people think and the barriers people put up for themselves when they attempt to learn another language. Having this understanding allows me to be able to put the student at ease and help them feel more confident in their ability to speak.

So, if you'd like to start speaking with a teacher who knows how it feels to try speaking a foreign language and someone who will care about your progress and whether you succeed or not then I am definitely the right teacher for you!

Let's get to know each other, become friends, trust each other and really improve your ability to communicate in English well.

*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*

Hobbies & Interests:
I love singing. I sing a lot. I sing karaoke, I sing in the shower, I sing at home. I like the Beatles, Frank Sinatra, Dean Martin, Bobby Darin, Nat King Cole, Elton John, Elvis Presley, Michael Jackson - I have a very eclectic taste in music.

Maybe if you're lucky I will sing for you in a lesson! You can sing too if you want!

I read a lot. Auto-biographies, history books, novels, magazines. I love the escapism of reading and that it can transport you to another place and time.

I love to play rugby and I was a good player when I was younger. It's quite a physical game and looks like it hurts a lot, but it's very exciting when you play!

I also follow snooker and I am big fan of the Chinese player Ding Junhui and England's Ronnie O'Sullivan. Ding is very talented and I watch him whenever I can.

I love animals and am a firm supporter of animal welfare programs.

I also follow global current affairs and read all news from all places.

无论你想学英语或者其他语言，你必须要有一个积极的态度。积极的态度在学习的过程中会起到非常重要的作用，也会让你因为获得知识而感到兴奋。

敲钉子要敲在它扁平的顶部，意思是说做事情要正确且精准，这是我最信奉的话。我在网上教英文已经2年了，我的经验和专业能让我有能力帮助到个个水平的学生。曾在迪拜工作超过五年的时间，基本上都是和英国，美国和其他中东国家的人一起共事。也曾游历过许多中东国家。

我喜欢看电影，演唱会，听音乐，弹钢琴等等。我是吃货还是大厨？应该都算！哈哈 

有任何问题都可以找我，没有任何话题的拘束，期待你的来电，做我的vip吧！
